let leftArrow = {
  width: "0px", 
  height: "0px", 
  borderTop: "10px solid transparent", 
  borderBottom: "10px solid transparent", 
  borderRight: "10px solid #4382BC", 
  marginTop: "10px",
  marginRight: "15px",
  cursor: "pointer"
}

let rightArrow = {
  width: "0px", 
  height: "0px", 
  borderTop: "10px solid transparent", 
  borderBottom: "10px solid transparent", 
  borderLeft: "10px solid #4382BC", 
  marginTop: "10px",
  marginLeft: "5px",
  cursor: "pointer"
}

let pageNumber = {
  width: "16px",
  margin: "8px 10px 0px 2px",
  cursor: "pointer", 
  color: "#4382BC",
  textAlign: "center",
  userSelect: "none"
}

let firstPage = {
  width: "16px",
  margin: "8px 8px 0px 0px",
  cursor: "pointer", 
  color: "white",
  userSelect: "none"
}

let lastPage = {
  width: "16px",
  margin: "8px 10px 0px 1px",
  cursor: "pointer", 
  color: "#4382BC",
  userSelect: "none"
}

let leftTab = {
  margin: "6px 4px 0px -6px",
  color: "#4382BC",
  visibility: "hidden",
  userSelect: "none"
}

let rightTab = {
  margin: "6px 7px 0px 0px",
  color: "#4382BC",
  visibility: "visible",
  userSelect: "none"
}

export {
  leftArrow,
  rightArrow,
  pageNumber,
  firstPage,
  lastPage,
  leftTab,
  rightTab
}
